---
import Card from "./Card/index.astro";
---

<Card colSpan="md:col-span-1" rowSpan="md:row-span-6" title="About me">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 about-text">
    <p class="sr-only">
      Hi, I'm Sodiq Ardianto, a software developer from Indonesia with a strong
      foundation in backend development using Laravel and Express, frontend
      technologies like React and Next.js, and mobile development with Flutter.
      I enjoy building scalable systems, applying DRY and SOLID principles to
      craft clean, maintainable code, and ensuring great user experiences. I
      also have solid experience utilizing Linux and Docker to streamline
      development and deployment workflows, along with databases like MySQL and
      PostgreSQL. I believe in choosing the right tools for the job and
      continuously improving through learning.
    </p>
    <div aria-hidden="true" class="text-sm font-light">
      <p class="text-sm font-light">
        Hi, I'm Sodiq Ardianto, a software developer from Indonesia.
      </p>
      <br />
      My primary tools of choice include:
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
        <li>Laravel & PHP</li>
        <li>Express & Node.js</li>
        <li>React & Next.js</li>
        <li>Flutter</li>
        <li>Linux & Docker</li>
        <li>MySQL & PostgreSQL</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm font-light mt-4">
      I focus on building robust backend APIs, clean user interfaces, and
      engaging mobile apps. In my work, I strive to write maintainable code by
      naturally adopting SOLID and DRY principles into my architecture. I'm
      passionate about modernizing workflows and using tools that improve
      efficiency and developer experience.
    </p>
  </div>
</Card>

<style>
  /* Make about text black in dark mode (default state) */
  .about-text {
    color: #ffffff !important;
  }

  /* Make about text white in light mode */
  :global(.light-mode) .about-text {
    color: #000000 !important;
  }

  /* Ensure bold text maintains proper contrast */
  .about-text b {
    color: inherit;
  }
</style>
